description: Normally, at least 80% of the fund's total assets (exclusive of collateral held from securities lending) will be invested in component securities of the index and investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the economic characteristics of such component securities. The index is a modified float-adjusted market cap weighted index that consists of companies incorporated and traded in India, excluding common stocks of "state-owned enterprises." The fund is non-diversified.
name: WisdomTree India ex-State-Owned Enterprises Fund
